sourcesContent: import*as r from"react";import{ComponentClassNames as e}from"../shared/constants.js";import"tslib";import"classnames";import"../View/View.js";import{IconCheckCircle as n}from"../Icon/icons/IconCheckCircle.js";import{IconError as o}from"../Icon/icons/IconError.js";import{IconInfo as a}from"../Icon/icons/IconInfo.js";import{IconWarning as c}from"../Icon/icons/IconWarning.js";const s=({variation:s,ariaHidden:t})=>{switch(s){case"info":return r.createElement(a,{"aria-hidden":t,className:e.AlertIcon});case"error":return r.createElement(o,{"aria-hidden":t,className:e.AlertIcon});case"warning":return r.createElement(c,{"aria-hidden":t,className:e.AlertIcon});case"success":return r.createElement(n,{"aria-hidden":t,className:e.AlertIcon});default:return null}};s.displayName="AlertIcon";export{s as AlertIcon};
